<body>

<div class=3D"container">
    <header>
        <div class=3D"subtitle">Software Progress Report</div>
        <h1>What can the Autolinium App do today?</h1>
    </header>

    <div class=3D"feature-item">
        <div class=3D"icon-circle">1</div>
        <div class=3D"feature-content">
            <h2>Secure Digital Entry</h2>
            <p>Every employee has their own account. Admin sees everything,=
 staff only see their own work. Your company data is locked and safe.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"feature-item">
        <div class=3D"icon-circle">2</div>
        <div class=3D"feature-content">
            <h2>One-Tap Attendance</h2>
            <p>Staff check-in and check-out with a single tap on their phon=
es. No more manual registers or messy paperwork.</p>
            <span class=3D"badge">Fully Functional</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"feature-item">
        <div class=3D"icon-circle">3</div>
        <div class=3D"feature-content">
            <h2>Live Work Timer</h2>
            <p>The app automatically tracks exactly how many hours everyone=
 has worked today. It flags late-comers automatically after 11:00 AM.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"feature-item">
        <div class=3D"icon-circle">4</div>
        <div class=3D"feature-content">
            <h2>Digital Leave Requests</h2>
            <p>Instead of phone calls or texts, staff ask for days off thro=
ugh the app. They can list the reason and the dates clearly.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"feature-item">
        <div class=3D"icon-circle">5</div>
        <div class=3D"feature-content">
            <h2>Manager's Control Panel</h2>
            <p>The Boss has a special "Dashboard" to see everyone's attenda=
nce. You can approve or reject leave requests with a single click.</p>
            <span class=3D"badge">Fully Functional</span>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"feature-item">
        <div class=3D"icon-circle">6</div>
        <div class=3D"feature-content">
            <h2>Performance Scoring (KPI)</h2>
            <p>The system automatically gives staff points for being on tim=
e. This helps you see who is dedicated and who is consistently late without=
 checking logs manually.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"feature-item">
        <div class=3D"icon-circle">7</div>
        <div class=3D"feature-content">
            <h2>Task Management</h2>
            <p>You can assign specific tasks to different staff members. Th=
ey mark them "Done" in the app so you know the status of work in real-time.=
</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"summary" style=3D"margin-top: 20px; background: #fffbeb; =
border-color: #fde68a;">
        <h3 style=3D"color: #92400e;">=F0=9F=93=8A Direct Database Records<=
/h3>
        <p style=3D"font-size: 0.9rem; color: #92400e;">For complete transp=
arency, the following data is captured instantly in the system database:</p=
>
        <ul style=3D"font-size: 0.9rem; color: #92400e; padding-left: 20px;=
 margin-top: 10px;">
            <li><b>Exact Timestamps:</b> Every check-in and check-out time =
is recorded to the second.</li>
            <li><b>Manager Decisions:</b> Every leave approval or rejection=
 is logged with the manager's name.</li>
            <li><b>Score History:</b> Monthly KPI points and attendance gra=
des are saved permanently.</li>
            <li><b>Task Logs:</b> Who completed what task and when is track=
ed for performance reviews.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"summary">
        <h3>Summary for Management</h3>
        <p>The software is now at a stage where it can completely replace m=
anual attendance and leave tracking. It ensures staff are accountable for t=
heir time and gives you total control over approvals and task monitoring.</=
p>
    </div>

    <footer>
        Generated for Management Review =E2=80=A2 March 3, 2026
    </footer>
</div>



</body></html>
